      • getSparkMaster

        public String getSparkMaster()
        If the Spark master is set in this class then that will be used. Otherwise the Spark default config set on the local machine will be used, if you run your code as a spark-submit command or from the spark-shell. Otherwise a local Spark master will be used.
        Returns:
        The Spark master to be used.
